examples.en: The beam holds up the roof.
This box holds a pound of candy.
He holds the record in the mile.
He holds a 51% stake in the firm.
This room holds a hundred people.
Each milk crate holds nine bottles.
That bank holds the mortgage on my home.
He holds a 30% interest in the gold mine.
She holds a commanding lead in the polls.
She holds a Master's degree from Harvard.
